  "original_title": "\u0dc3\u0db8\u0dca\u0db7\u0dcf\u0dc4\u0db1 \u0db8\u0db0\u0dca\u200d\u0dba\u0dc3\u0dca\u0dae\u0dcf\u0db1\u0dba\u0dda \u0dc4\u0dd2\u0db8\u0dd2\u0d9a\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dba\u0da7 \u0d9c\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dd2 \u0dad\u0db6\u0dcf \u0d9d\u0dcf\u0dad\u0db1\u0dba \u0d9a\u0dbb\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The owner of a massage parlor is set on fire and killed",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A group of persons had entered a massage center in Habarana town and had assaulted its employees with sticks, setting fire to the owner of the massage center and seriously injuring him.",
        "The injured woman was admitted to the Dambulla Hospital and succumbed to her injuries yesterday morning.",
        "The deceased has been identified as a 28 year old resident of Madura Road, Pradeshiya Sabha. The attack and the killing were the result of a long-running dispute with a group of people who had come to work at the massage center. A suspect arrested in connection with the incident has been remanded till the 7th of this month after being produced before court."
      ],
